textfsm_template:
Value FAN_TRAY (\d+)
Value FAN (\d+)
Value STATUS (OK|Failed)
Value SPEED (\d+ RPM)

Start
  ^Fan Tray:\s+${FAN_TRAY}\s*$$ -> FanTray
  ^Fan:\s+${FAN}\s*$$ -> Fan

FanTray
  ^\s*Fan:\s+${FAN}\s*$$ -> Fan
  ^\s*$$ -> Start

Fan
  ^\s*Status:\s+${STATUS}\s*$$
  ^\s*Speed:\s+${SPEED}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*$$ -> Start
